---
import BankingLayout from '@layouts/BankingLayout.astro';
import SimpleButton from '@components/Button/SimpleButton.astro';
---

<BankingLayout title="About Kleva - AI Collections for LATAM" description="How we're solving the $67 billion collections problem in Latin America">
  <main class="about-page">
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="page-title">The Story Behind Kleva</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">
          We discovered a $67 billion problem in LATAM that nobody wants to talk about. 
          Now we're solving it with AI.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="story-block">
          <h2>The Discovery</h2>
          <p>
            Six months ago, we were building restaurant agents. Then we met Tito, CEO of Vana, 
            a microloan company in Guatemala. He showed us something shocking: 
            <strong>60% of his company—over 200 employees—were doing collections.</strong>
          </p>
          <p>
            "This is one of the few opportunities where you can match work directly to ROI," 
            Tito told us. "Every dollar collected is measurable. As long as you integrate properly, 
            you'll always justify the service."
          </p>
          <p>
            He was right. We pivoted immediately.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="story-block">
          <h2>The Surprise</h2>
          <p>
            We thought we'd just save Vana money by automating calls. But our AI agents were 
            actually <strong>better at recovering money than humans</strong>. Not just cheaper. Better.
          </p>
          <div class="results-grid">
            <div class="result-card">
              <span class="result-number">25%</span>
              <span class="result-label">Higher Recovery</span>
            </div>
            <div class="result-card">
              <span class="result-number">70%</span>
              <span class="result-label">Cost Reduction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="result-card">
              <span class="result-number">0%</span>
              <span class="result-label">Agent Turnover</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>
            But here's what really shocked us: <strong>Debtors preferred talking to our AI.</strong> 
            Why? Because AI has infinite patience. It never shames. It offers solutions, not threats.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="story-block">
          <h2>The Mission</h2>
          <p>
            We're not just building another collections tool. We're building the 
            <strong>AI workforce for LATAM's financial industry</strong>.
          </p>
          <p>
            Starting with collections—the hardest, most painful role in banking. 
            After we perfect this, we'll expand to dispute resolution, fraud prevention, 
            and credit review. Eventually, every repetitive financial services role will 
            have a Kleva AI agent that does it better, cheaper, 24/7.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="team-section">
          <h2>The Team Making It Happen</h2>
          <div class="team-grid">
            <div class="team-card">
              <h3>Gonza</h3>
              <span class="role">Product Owner</span>
              <p>Lives in customer data, ensuring we add value every single day.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-card">
              <h3>Santi</h3>
              <span class="role">Lead Developer</span>
              <p>Obsesses over making conversations feel natural, not robotic.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-card">
              <h3>Os</h3>
              <span class="role">Infrastructure</span>
              <p>Built systems handling thousands of simultaneous calls without breaking.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-card">
              <h3>Lila</h3>
              <span class="role">Problem Solver</span>
              <p>Achieved 94% address accuracy in LATAM (vs Google's 70%).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-card">
              <h3>Juli</h3>
              <span class="role">Quality & AI</span>
              <p>Reviews every call, building AI that automatically improves.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-card">
              <h3>JM</h3>
              <span class="role">Cofounder</span>
              <p>Gets customers to their "wow moment" in days, not months.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="investment-block">
          <h2>We're All In</h2>
          <p>
            We believed in this vision so much that we funded it ourselves. 
            <strong>Over $100K of our own money</strong> invested into developing the technology, 
            refining the AI, and getting clients live. No outside investors, no dilution, 
            just pure conviction.
          </p>
          <p>
            We bootstrapped our way to <strong>$150K MRR by December</strong>. 
            Now, with proven results and a massive pipeline, it's time to scale.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-section">
          <h2>Join the Revolution</h2>
          <p>
            Every day we wait, 10,000 collections agents burn out. Millions of debtors get 
            harassed instead of helped. Billions stay locked in bad debt.
          </p>
          <p>
            We've built the solution. We've proven it works. Our clients love it. 
            Their customers prefer it.
          </p>
          <SimpleButton href="/contact" size="lg">
            Transform Your Collections
          </SimpleButton>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BankingLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding-top: var(--header-height-mobile);
  }

  .hero-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3730a3 100%);
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .content-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .story-block {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .story-block h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .story-block p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #4b5563;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .story-block strong {
    color: #111827;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .results-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .result-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe 0%, #e0e7ff 100%);
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }

  .result-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1e3a8a;
  }

  .result-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #3730a3;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .team-section {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .team-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #111827;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .team-card {
    background: #f9fafb;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .team-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .role {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #3730a3;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .team-card p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .investment-block {
    background: #fef3c7;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .investment-block h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #78350f;
  }

  .investment-block p {
    color: #92400e;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .investment-block strong {
    color: #78350f;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: #f9fafb;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: #4b5563;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-page {
      padding-top: var(--header-height-desktop);
    }
  }
</style>